1. *Napustili* smo grad u zoru. (We left the city at dawn.)
2. Oni su već *napustili* ovaj projekat. (They have already abandoned this project.)
3. Kada su *napustili* kuću, setili su se da su zaboravili ključeve. (When they left the house, they remembered that they forgot the keys.)
4. Danas su mnogi zaposleni *napustili* firmu zbog loših uslova rada. (Today, many employees have left the company due to poor working conditions.)
5. Čim su *napustili* restoran, počeli su da se raspravljaju o kvalitetu hrane. (As soon as they left the restaurant, they started to argue about the quality of the food.)
6. *Napustili* su nas pre dve godine i od tada ih nismo videli. (They left us two years ago and we haven't seen them since.)
7. Kada su *napustili* zemlju, osećali su se olakšano. (When they left the country, they felt relieved.)
8. Nisu mogli da veruju da su *napustili* decu kod kuće samu. (They couldn't believe that they left the kids home alone.)
9. *Napustili* su svoje snove zbog praktičnosti. (They abandoned their dreams for practicality.)
10. Pre nego što su *napustili* sobu, ugasili su svetlo. (Before leaving the room, they turned off the light.)